Package es.usc.citius.lab.joctomap.util

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdjacencyMap
    This class implements a builder for calculating the adjacency map of an Octomap.
    CollisionChecker2D
    This class implements a collision checker which uses native methods to determine the collision in a 2D octree using 2D shapes (circular and rectangular).
    JOctreeUtils
    Contains utilities implemented for the JOctree, but not included in the C/C++ implementation of Octomap.
    NativeObject
    Represents an object that supports native calls.
    NativeUtils
    Simple library class for working with JNI (Java Native Interface)
    Obstacle
    Class defining an obstacle, formed by a 3D point and the distance.
    PPMFileReader
    Class which parses a PPM file (ASCII format).
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    JOctomapLogger
    Custom class to extend the capabilities of Logger for the JOctomap library.
